data.enText: one thing on a list of things to buy, do, talk about, etc.
What's the next item on the agenda?

data.chText: 我能否一件一件地分别付钱？
data.enText: Can I pay for each item separately?

data.chText: 电脑是我花钱最多的一件东西。
data.enText: The computer was my largest single item of expenditure.
This clock is a collector's item (= because it is rare and valuable) .
a single piece of news in a newspaper, on television, etc.
an item of news/a news item
to be involved in a romantic or sexual relationship

ex.en: agenda item ( or item on an agenda)

data.enText: to be involved in a romantic or sexual relationship

tr: especially when included in a list or collection
example: they reduced the price on many items

tr: an isolated fact that is considered separately from the whole
example: several of the details are similar

tr: a distinct part that can be specified separately in a group of things that could be enumerated on a list
example: he noticed an item in the New York Times
she had several items on her shopping list
the main point on the agenda was taken up first

tr: an individual instance of a type of symbol
example: the word`error' contains three tokens of `r'

tr: a small part that can be considered separately from the whole
example: it was perfect in all details

tr: (used when listing or enumerating items) also
example: a length of chain, item a hook"-Philip Guedall

value.def: An item is one of a collection or list of objects.

example.ex: The most valuable item on show will be a Picasso drawing...
example.tran: 展览会上最贵重的展品是毕加索的一幅素描。

example.ex: The menu includes the occasional off-beat item.
example.tran: 菜单中包括了偶尔会有的非传统菜肴。

value.def: An item is one of a list of things for someone to do, deal with, or talk about.

example.ex: The other item on the agenda is the tour.
example.tran: 日程中的另一项是旅游。

value.def: An item is a report or article in a newspaper or magazine, or on television or radio.

example.ex: There was an item in the paper about him.
example.tran: 报纸上有一条关于他的报道。

value.tran: 一篇报道(或文章);(新闻等的)一条,一则

value.def: If you say that two people are an item, you mean that they are having a romantic or sexual relationship.

example.ex: She and Gino were an item.
